From: Daniel Mack <daniel@zonque.org>
Date: Mon, 28 May 2018 21:53:38 +0200
Subject: drm/msm: call drm_atomic_helper_suspend() and
 drm_atomic_helper_resume()
Git-commit: ec446d09366cea199214b30810e368c5178841cd
Patch-mainline: v4.19-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

To make suspend and resume work on msm8916 platforms, call into the generic
helpers and preserve the state across suspends.

Signed-off-by: Daniel Mack <daniel@zonque.org>
Signed-off-by: Rob Clark <robdclark@gmail.com>
Acked-by: Petr Tesarik <ptesarik@suse.com>
